  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of HL-040XC in Essential Hypertension and Hyperlipidemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Randomized, Double- Blind, Multi-center, Double Dummy, Clinical Trial Comparing HL-040XC With Single Component Therapies(Atorvastatin, Losartan) to Assess the Efficacy and Safety of HL-040XC in Patients With Essential Hypertension and Hyperlipidemia</official_title>
